From daf13175d10eda11bfd024bfc50de6806ea8e7ed Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Developer <noreply@example.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 10:51:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add demo-brand-explorer block based on skyrizihcp.com brand
 explorer

Multi-brand product navigator accordion with fixed bottom bar, 3-column
grid panel with brand logos, severity-prefixed indication links, and
mobile accordion behavior. Includes UE component models and brand
override scaffolds for abbvie, botox, and rinvoq.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
